sentences: Shawn Moltke  (born September 6, 1965) better known by his stage name MC Shan, is an American hip hop and R&B recording artist.
In 1985, Shan started on MCA Records with his first and only MCA single, "Feed the World".

His debut album Down by Law was released on Warner Bros in 1987.
